  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package contains a broken provenance link: the primary hemolysis validation result carries detailed narrative describing the CFD–experiment comparison campaign but omits the structured prov:wasGeneratedBy activity reference, triggering W-EP-02.",
